#. <html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta content="Pali text from the Mahāsaṅgīti Tipiṭaka Buddhavasse 2500" name="description"><title></title></head><body><div id="text" lang="pli"><section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs0.3"
msgid "Aniyatakaṇḍa"
msgstr "Monks’ Undetermined"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs0.4"
msgid "1. Paṭhamaaniyatasikkhāpada"
msgstr "1. The first training rule"

#. </h1></div><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.187"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.330"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1802"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs0.5"
msgid "Ime kho panāyasmanto dve aniyatā dhammā"
msgstr "Venerables, these two undetermined rules"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs0.6"
msgid "uddesaṃ āgacchanti."
msgstr "come up for recitation."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.1.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1803"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī sāvatthiyaṃ kulūpako hoti, bahukāni "
"kulāni upasaṅkamati."
msgstr ""
"At that time Venerable Udāyī was associating with and visiting a number of "
"families in Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato udāyissa upaṭṭhākakulassa kumārikā "
"aññatarassa kulassa kumārakassa dinnā hoti."
msgstr ""
"One of those families had given their daughter in marriage to the son of "
"another family."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā udāyī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena taṃ "
"kulaṃ tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr ""
"Just then, after robing up one morning, Venerable Udāyī took his bowl and "
"robe and went to the first of those families."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.5"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā manusse pucchi—"
msgstr "When he arrived, he asked"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.6"
msgid "“kahaṃ itthannāmā”ti?"
msgstr "where the daughter was,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.7"
msgid "Te evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "and he was told"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.8"
msgid "“dinnā, bhante, amukassa kulassa kumārakassā”ti."
msgstr "that she had been given to another family."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.9"
msgid "Tampi kho kulaṃ āyasmato udāyissa upaṭṭhākaṃ hoti."
msgstr "That family too supported Venerable Udāyī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.10"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā udāyī yena taṃ kulaṃ tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "He then went there"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.11"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā manusse pucchi—"
msgstr "and again asked"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.12"
msgid "“kahaṃ itthannāmā”ti?"
msgstr "where the girl was."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.13"
msgid "Te evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "They said,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.14"
msgid "“esāyya, ovarake nisinnā”ti."
msgstr "“She’s sitting in her room.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.15"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā udāyī yena sā kumārikā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "He approached that girl,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.16"
msgid ""
"upasaṅkamitvā tassā kumārikāya saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane "
"alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappesi kālayuttaṃ samullapanto kālayuttaṃ dhammaṃ "
"bhaṇanto."
msgstr ""
"and the two of them sat down alone on a private and concealed seat suitable "
"for doing it. When they were able, they just chatted; otherwise he gave her "
"a teaching."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.188"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1804"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.331"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.17"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena visākhā migāramātā bahuputtā hoti bahunattā "
"arogaputtā aroganattā abhimaṅgalasammatā."
msgstr ""
"At that time Visākhā Migāramātā had many healthy children and grandchildren, "
"and she was considered very auspicious."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.18"
msgid ""
"Manussā yaññesu chaṇesu ussavesu visākhaṃ migāramātaraṃ paṭhamaṃ bhojenti."
msgstr ""
"At sacrifices, festivals, and celebrations people would feed Visākhā first."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.19"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā nimantitā taṃ kulaṃ agamāsi."
msgstr ""
"Just then she had been invited to the family that supported Venerable Udāyī."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.20"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho visākhā migāramātā āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ tassā kumārikāya saddhiṃ "
"ekaṃ ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisinnaṃ."
msgstr "When she arrived, she saw him sitting alone with that girl,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.21"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "and she said to him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.22"
msgid ""
"“idaṃ, bhante, nacchannaṃ nappatirūpaṃ yaṃ ayyo mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya "
"raho paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappeti."
msgstr ""
"“Venerable, it’s not appropriate that you should sit alone with a woman on a "
"private and concealed seat suitable for doing it."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.23"
msgid ""
"Kiñcāpi, bhante, ayyo anatthiko tena dhammena, api ca dussaddhāpayā "
"appasannā manussā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Although you may not be aiming at that act, people with little confidence "
"are hard to convince.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.24"
msgid "Evampi kho āyasmā udāyī visākhāya migāramātuyā vuccamāno nādiyi."
msgstr "But Udāyī did not listen."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.25"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā nikkhamitvā bhikkhūnaṃ etamatthaṃ ārocesi."
msgstr "After leaving, Visākhā told the monks about what had happened."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.26"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.27"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.28"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma āyasmā udāyī mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne "
"āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappessatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“How can Venerable Udāyī sit alone with a woman on a private and concealed "
"seat suitable for doing it?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1805"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.29"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato "
"etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After rebuking Udāyī in many ways, they told the Master …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.30"
msgid ""
"“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, udāyi, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne "
"āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappesī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Is it true, Udāyī, that you sat alone with a woman on a private and "
"concealed seat suitable for doing it?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.31"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.32"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.33"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho "
"paṭicchanne āsane alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappessasi."
msgstr "Foolish man, how can you sit alone with a woman on a such a seat?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.34"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.35"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.35a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1806"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.332"></a>
#. <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.36"
msgid ""
"“Yo pana bhikkhu mātugāmena saddhiṃ eko ekāya raho paṭicchanne āsane "
"alaṃkammaniye nisajjaṃ kappeyya, tamenaṃ saddheyyavacasā upāsikā disvā "
"tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena vadeyya—"
msgstr ""
"‘If a monk sits alone with a woman on a private and concealed seat suitable "
"for doing it, and a trustworthy female lay follower sees him and accuses him"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.37"
msgid ""
"pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā, nisajjaṃ bhikkhu "
"paṭijānamāno tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr ""
"of an offense entailing expulsion or an offense entailing suspension or an "
"offense entailing confession, then, if he admits to the sitting, he is to be "
"dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.38"
msgid ""
"pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā, yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā "
"upāsikā vadeyya, tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
msgstr ""
"according to one of these three or according to what that trustworthy female "
"lay follower has said."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.39"
msgid "Ayaṃ dhammo aniyato”ti."
msgstr "This rule is undetermined.’”"

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs1.40"
msgid "(<em>1</em>:<strong>18</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="pts-cs-empty" id="bu-an.1.2"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.1.2.1"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1807"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever …"

#. </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""
"… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order "
"through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is "
"unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1808"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.6"
msgid "Mātugāmo nāma"
msgstr "A woman:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.7"
msgid "manussitthī, na yakkhī na petī na tiracchānagatā."
msgstr ""
"a human female, not a female spirit, not a female ghost, not a female animal;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.8"
msgid "Antamaso tadahujātāpi dārikā, pageva mahattarī."
msgstr "even a girl born that very day, all the more an older one."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1809"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.9"
msgid "Saddhinti"
msgstr "With:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.10"
msgid "ekato."
msgstr "together."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1810"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.11"
msgid "Eko ekāyāti"
msgstr "Alone:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.12"
msgid "bhikkhu ceva hoti mātugāmo ca."
msgstr "just the monk and the woman."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1811"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.13"
msgid "Raho nāma"
msgstr "Private:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.14"
msgid "cakkhussa raho, sotassa raho."
msgstr "there is private to the eye and there is private to the ear."

#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.15"
msgid "Cakkhussa raho nāma"
msgstr "Private to the eye"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.16"
msgid ""
"na sakkā hoti akkhiṃ vā nikhaṇīyamāne bhamukaṃ vā ukkhipīyamāne sīsaṃ vā "
"ukkhipīyamāne passituṃ."
msgstr "one is unable to see them winking, raising an eyebrow, or nodding."

#. </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.17"
msgid "Sotassa raho nāma"
msgstr "Private to the ear"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.18"
msgid "na sakkā hoti pakatikathā sotuṃ."
msgstr "one is unable to hear ordinary speech."

#. </span></span></p><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.189"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1812"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.19"
msgid "Paṭicchannaṃ nāma"
msgstr "Concealed seat:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
#. VAR: kuṭṭena vā → kuḍḍena vā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.20"
msgid ""
"āsanaṃ kuṭṭena vā kavāṭena vā kilañjena vā sāṇipākārena vā rukkhena vā "
"thambhena vā kotthaḷiyā vā yena kenaci paṭicchannaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"it is concealed by a wall, a screen, a door, a screening cloth, a tree, a "
"pillar, a grain container, or anything else."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1813"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.333"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.21"
msgid "Alaṃkammaniyeti"
msgstr "Suitable for doing it:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.22"
msgid "sakkā hoti methunaṃ dhammaṃ paṭisevituṃ."
msgstr "one is able to have sexual intercourse."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1814"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.23"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ kappeyyāti"
msgstr "Sits:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.24"
msgid "mātugāme nisinne bhikkhu upanisinno vā hoti upanipanno vā."
msgstr "the monk sits down or lies down next to the seated woman."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.25"
msgid "Bhikkhu nisinne mātugāmo upanisinno vā hoti upanipanno vā."
msgstr "The woman sits down or lies down next to the seated monk."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.26"
msgid "Ubho vā nisinnā honti ubho vā nipannā."
msgstr "Both are seated or both are lying down."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1815"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.27"
msgid "Saddheyyavacasā nāma"
msgstr "Trustworthy:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.28"
msgid "āgataphalā abhisametāvinī viññātasāsanā."
msgstr ""
"she has attained the fruit, she has broken through, she has understood the "
"Teaching."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1816"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.29"
msgid "Upāsikā nāma"
msgstr "Female lay follower:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.30"
msgid "buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā, saṃghaṃ saraṇaṃ gatā."
msgstr "she has gone for refuge to the Buddha, the Teaching, and the Order."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1817"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.31"
msgid "Disvāti"
msgstr "Sees:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.1.32"
msgid "passitvā."
msgstr "having seen."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-an.1.2.2"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1818"></a><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.2.1"
msgid "Tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena vadeyya—"
msgstr "Accuses him of an offense"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.2.2"
msgid "pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr ""
"entailing expulsion or an offense entailing suspension or an offense "
"entailing confession,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.2.3"
msgid "Nisajjaṃ bhikkhu paṭijānamāno tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ aññatarena kāretabbo—"
msgstr "then, if he admits to the sitting, he is to be dealt with"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.2.4"
msgid "pārājikena vā saṃghādisesena vā pācittiyena vā."
msgstr "according to one of these three"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ay1:pts-cs2.2.5"
msgid "Yena vā sā saddheyyavacasā upāsikā vadeyya tena so bhikkhu kāretabbo."
